{"tid":1255926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[逆轉民意] 用孔子宣傳勇武","createTime":"2019-06-24T17:17:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T09:23:16.000Z","uid":267498,"like":236,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"811c374cb05272d94b13f0dd360dd2d4e3455f68","tid":1255926,"uid":267498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢輪開口埋口就民意逆轉<br />\n與其說服我地唔好衝<br />\n不如諗下點樣教化班和平人士<br />\n令佢地逐步認同</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>抗爭係可以升級</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n長遠計<br />\n政府一路漠視民意<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">行動向各個方向升級都係無可避免</span></strong><br />\n（人數、範圍、程度）<br />\n與其下下擔心民意逆轉<br />\n不如先教化民意<br />\n深化溫和派對政府嘅怨恨<br />\n等佢地明白「和平」喺呢個政府面前<br />\n係幾咁無用，幾咁垃圾，幾咁 R 痕<br />\n從而合理化勇武行為<br />\n<br />\n廢話少講<br />\n用圖交代 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttTfS5r.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttTfS5r.png&h=fe4185b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSyjAiN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSyjAiN.png&h=74be4cac&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFySViO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFySViO.png&h=03cad89e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFB <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/吾講吾德-389239205027484/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E5%90%BE%E8%AC%9B%E5%90%BE%E5%BE%B7-389239205027484%2F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=a9e29841\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/吾講吾德-389239205027484/</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/knowtalk_knowduck/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fknowtalk_knowduck%2F&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=9f1dd0e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/knowtalk_knowduck/</a><br />\nTG <a href=\"https://t.me/knowtalk_knowduck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fknowtalk_knowduck&d=%2Fh6QBFvJ2171tI4HayrYRp4W3gw9R4Gr2eBBN4Jm0fY%3D&h=4c1f11e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/knowtalk_knowduck</a><br />\n<br />\n用詩書同矯情推廣勇武<br />\n拉近溫和派同勇武嘅距離<br />\n<strong>歡迎偷圖 cap 圖 air drop 放送</strong><br />\n三個平台同步推廣，歡迎供稿<br />\n<br />\n諗三個已經好撚極限下<br />\n啲學養已經還返晒俾中學阿 sir<br />\n跪求中化撚提供更多 idea<br />\n<del>唔係講笑，真係諗多個都諗唔到</del><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddade88821177435229a8d1ff8db6d142ce3768c","tid":1255926,"uid":267498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"點先推到多啲人睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6dba9f709fbe682be0eafb1418f9b249983259","tid":1255926,"uid":267498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:18:31.000Z","msg":"點先推到多啲人睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11be2c5bd8be23d57333d06c526bb144a93ec87c","tid":1255926,"uid":267498,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T17:19:14.000Z","msg":"再沉就唔推了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8066b17affc4db152bc431e8016db9b6a8e632f","tid":1255926,"uid":267498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06